text: Fabrice LeClerc (born 28 April 1968) is a French rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Aube
